        <div class="msgSubject">Splintered Shadows</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2008-03-27 21:17:00 | Edited: Mar 27 2008  9:20pm  | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-1206681421308511161" id="quote-1206681421308511161" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-1206681421308511161" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/journal.html?user=672337&amp;mid=1206681421308511161&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=1206681421308511161&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_1206681421308511161" onclick="followToggle('add','1206681421308511161')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
